# Quick Start Guide - AZ-204

## ?? Getting Started

### Prerequisites
```powershell
# 1. Install Azure CLI
winget install -e --id Microsoft.AzureCLI

# 2. Close and reopen PowerShell!

# 3. Verify
az --version

# 4. Login
az login
```

**?? Quick Check:** Run `.\install-prerequisites.ps1` to verify everything is ready!

---

## ?? Step-by-Step Deployments (NEW!)

Deploy Azure services one at a time. Learn as you go!

### ? Deployment Order:

```powershell
# 1. SETUP (Required - Run First!)
.\deploy-0-setup.ps1
# Creates resource group, generates unique names

# 2. APP SERVICE (Web Apps)
.\deploy-1-appservice.ps1
# Time: 5 min | Cost: $2/day

# 3. FUNCTIONS (Serverless)
.\deploy-2-functions.ps1
# Time: 5 min | Cost: $0-5/day

# 4. CONTAINER INSTANCES
.\deploy-3-container-instances.ps1
# Time: 2 min | Cost: $1/day

# 5. AKS (Optional - Expensive!)
.\deploy-4-aks.ps1
# Time: 20 min | Cost: $150/month ??

# 6. SUPPORTING SERVICES (Optional)
.\deploy-5-supporting-services.ps1
# Time: 15 min | Cost: $2/day

# 7. OUTPUT CONFIG (Required - Run Last!)
.\deploy-6-output-config.ps1
# Generates appsettings.json
```

---

